item.title: Senna's Legacy - The NSX - Honda-Tech
item.description:
Senna's Legacy - The NSX - Honda-Tech

Filmmaker Robert Albalas has put together two short films encapsulating the spirit of the original NSX. Conceived in the 1980's, the NSX was being developed at a high point for the Honda brand. In addition to being a winning engine supplier in Formula 1, the pinnacle of motorsport, the brand was also branching out commercially.
